Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery's pretty invigorating, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.60,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yunosagi's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll be able to take \Nsome great pictures here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:10.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Isami speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They've just opened up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yunosagi Cirrus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they've already got \Nso many customers, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 16\NThat Sky, This Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Fukuya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.75,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I've now heard everyone's opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.85,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Any other thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.52,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what the younger generation expects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from a hot spring inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:42.74,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.14,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who said \Nwe only had to sit here and do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.44,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Give us your honest opinions please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.69,Default,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think it ought to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,full of food you want to \Neat yet be cheap as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A cheap all-you-can-eat \Nbuffet that serves meat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cake from morning to evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and maybe a luxurious coach,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is comfortable enough to sleep in, \Nthat drops you off at Yunosagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:16.43,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,O-oh, I think an indoor pool that uses\Nwater from the hot spring would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! A pool is an absolute necessity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:22.53,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,There may be guests \Nthat want to swim at all hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.01,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It would be awesome if the coaches \Nserved cake on board too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.14,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everything's prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.15,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's present this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Madam Manger, young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.05,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.40,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.58,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,How's the inn supposed to run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when its own young master \Nlacks self-confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.12,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,An important factor in giving a convincing presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.23,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,is that the presenter themselves are motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll understand \Nhow much we respect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso after she hears our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.79,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Now come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.63,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, this inn is really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.33,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.37,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso will only need to invest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a tenth of the production cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.30,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! It'll work like magic-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.73,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,The benefits gained from the advertising will be huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.13,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,The masses of people who watch the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will all want to stay at this inn at least once,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.87,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,and as a consequence, \Nthey'll all visit Yunosagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:38.36,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, none of this is guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.99,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,But from my experience, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:44.43,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to speak with \Nthe young master in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.31,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.10,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I join the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:52.89,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd like Takako to join our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.43,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.00,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.00,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you to have this \Nconversation in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.20,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What have you got planned, Nakochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.26,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the beach \Nwith my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.63,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be working here \Nthe whole summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.22,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then let's go to \Nthe beach together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:22.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd love to meet your brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.38,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goodness! You've got to hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.71,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's a movie! A movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.60,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.56,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,They're filming a movie at Kissuiso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.21,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.52,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.91,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go home and tell my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.85,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.44,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what part \NI'm going to be playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.54,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.53,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.74,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.93,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.45,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.63,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the whole of Yunosagi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will gradually become \Npoorer and poorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.92,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked when
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako asked whether we wanted \Nto be filmed or not, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.32,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.19,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.20,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow you free reign to do \Nwhat you want this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.78,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:38.38,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, due to a strongly-worded \Nrequest from the director,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.46,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,we're thinking about offering you roles in the film,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they're big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to hold a small audition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the director comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.56,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it's going to \Nbe an amazing summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.52,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play a great female spy who's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an ex-Olympic high diver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.14,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minchi, what kind of role do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.70,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,A chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But we're acting in a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A female police officer, a cabin attendant, a nurse-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.91,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a perverted old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.83,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.86,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you've left the young master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in charge of the \Ninvestment for the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:30.95,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.24,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,A movie... how wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:38.78,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko Kaga from {\i1}Withered \NFlower{\i0} was very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.98,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you still aren't \Nwithered, are you, Denroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.32,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.12,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you because you're
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dedicated enough to relocate to the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,countryside in order to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.38,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to write 40 pages
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take up 10 minutes of the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.76,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Please write us a scene that shows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the real warmth of this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.99,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,When do I get the chance to talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the director and the \Nmain writer about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.30,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll give you an outline \Nof the basic setting and plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you mind writing something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a springboard for discussion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.25,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then take that and \Ntalk to the director about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:17.51,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.86,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.56,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that there's this event
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called a "Bonbori Festival" \Nthat takes place around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.73,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,How about getting a \Ndescription of that? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.22,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jiromaru, the young master \Nspecifically requested that they
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,include your writing in the film \Nas a condition of the investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.99,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.07,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.06,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be checking the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,actual operational portions of the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What I need you all to \Ndo is brush up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This... is a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.24,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it used to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.49,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.81,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you want us to clean this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.19,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The pool must be used in the film as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.12,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's another condition imposed by \Nthe young master for the investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.40,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to say, \Nyoung master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.88,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,This place is scheduled to be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an important stage \Nfor the upcoming film,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.84,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,so please ensure \Nthat it's left sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But why the pool in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.16,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.87,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summer film!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.38,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Summer means the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.12,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The pool means summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:32.40,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,And... I wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.72,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Party... Party...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.27,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Addicted to parties!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.45,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.10,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how to \Nbegin to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.01,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me such a \Ngreat chance-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.92,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Those who work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be granted an opportunity as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.15,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.70,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.48,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We've both worked \Nso hard up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.40,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.14,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a hard life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, there were times \Nwe struggled shamelessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.26,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Helplessly flailing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.36,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.77,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:49.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,This small yet absolute \Nflame in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:53.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,tells us that what we've been \Ndoing hasn't been in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.58,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:56.70,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.16,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're also going to be taking half of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.21,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,manuscript fee and the royalties as payment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the room you've been staying in for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:05.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.02,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.89,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you a call \Nsometime during the week,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and drop by again with the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.44,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Director Matsumura will be visiting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.88,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,His first work, {\i1}Wet Button{\i0}, was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:23.90,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,His second-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.17,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we'll also be bringing \Nthe two leads for the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.38,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,They'd like to see the inn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it takes place in as soon as they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.90,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.37,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to sign the \Ncontract then as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.21,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:41.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.69,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.32,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.69,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.96,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.59,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I be of assistance in her place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.12,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to lend you a hand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this brilliant idea of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.53,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The film will be a bigger success
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you make the entirety of Yunosagi its stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since business is pretty bad these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,we can split the cost of the investment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between all of the inns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that help Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.49,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.91,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.80,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.85,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your offer to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.96,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,but the location of the filming \Nwill be limited solely to Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't plan on changing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.76,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then why are we paying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to advertise Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:12.99,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I've been saying \Nthat you don't need to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.81,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.04,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, you've got to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:33.54,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when he turned \Ninto such a fine young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.76,Default,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how he's planned to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do everything on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, Kissuiso is responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.48,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he firmly rejected \Nthe offer from the other inns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.38,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.76,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The young master sure has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.66,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's more confident in himself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.99,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess men really do change \Nafter doing something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.99,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,A movie, eh... That's a giant bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.75,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,So, what role are \Nyou playing, Mr. Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.47,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ren is in it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.61,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The director wants people working \Nat the inn to be in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:23.94,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.77,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.09,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands have stopped moving, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.59,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.77,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guess I had better \Nhead back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.52,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to peel the white radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.27,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Tomoe mentioned it, \NTohru's also excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.33,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone so hyped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a chef going to \Ndo in a movie anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.24,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the feeling that \NTohru would look good on screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.71,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.15,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.46,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.99,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.43,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.51,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a movie's gotta have a crane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.01,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ms. Suehiro, the \Nlead actress of the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.52,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.61,Default,Suehiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I look forward to working with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Actresses are so different from \Nordinary people, aren't they, Nakochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:30.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That day, they started \Ndoing the test shoots...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.15,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.34,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought some cold tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.70,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.16,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This is a wonderful inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.50,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I really like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'd like to make a \Npersonal visit here sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.12,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite an old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's hard to \Nkeep everything down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.17,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was already 60 years old when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was passed down to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, 60 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,After such a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seams come apart \Nin places that can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.14,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.03,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.30,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Suehiro, I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you could give us an autograph
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which we could use to \Ndecorate the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.59,Default,Sue,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.41,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to hear that Madam Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,agreed to the filming in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.32,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard she gave her consent right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she really wanted a role in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.13,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:15.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the main \Ncharacter's place for now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.07,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for the camera test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.18,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.29,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,The main character's running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as an additional benefit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You can walk arm-in-arm \Nwith Ms. Suehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A just married couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.21,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Show us what you've got, young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.43,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.33,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.51,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.86,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get a little closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:55.51,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The director insisted on someone \Nmore muscular for the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.09,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.68,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.00,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a short break...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:46.08,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, but we've gotten \Nthis place pretty clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a lot better than it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.75,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got a bit more to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, only a-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.19,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.83,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very thankful to you, Takako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.01,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely wouldn't have \Nbeen able to do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.86,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.84,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.52,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:40.86,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.19,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when we went
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the presentation for the \Nmovie the Film Club made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.53,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,During college, the fall \Nwhen you were a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.64,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.72,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.42,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.93,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that perverted film \Nthat only consisted of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clips of a middle school \Ngirl in a school swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that director would be \Nsent straight to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.55,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first piece of work as a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.41,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,First and last, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:30.82,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We were originally going to make a \Nlonger version of it at the Film Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:34.12,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,but the guy who was \Nsupposed to direct it quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.55,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That made all the other \Nmembers lose interest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.67,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I decided to film it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.57,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.20,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Something I experienced in my youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.52,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Are those girls doing their job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.96,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is definitely more suited
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to running Kissuiso than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.67,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.39,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Both my mother and I thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Shijima...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.61,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't called me \Nby that name since college!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.52,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.09,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:23.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's name is Satsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:26.89,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She's really quick-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:30.10,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She always talks in a precise, clipped style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.79,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's got charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.48,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She was really popular at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.34,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She looked so bright in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, intelligent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It was as though she was \Nliving in a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:47.42,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,A creature completely \Nunrelated to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.65,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't agree to that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:43.07,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:44.99,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished! The \Nmanuscript is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:47.23,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be finished like this! \NYou hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.90,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We shall return!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 17\NPool on the Hill
